data.description: Living is easy in this impressive,generously spacious residence 5 min distance from Galveston Bay.The open floor plan encompasses 4 spacious bedrooms with plenty of room for study,sleep and storage, 2 baths and 1/2, and a sleek and stylish gourmet kitchen that flows through the dinning room.The master bedroom, complete with walk-in closet,walk-in shower,and  tub.Never flooded.Highlight include fresh paint,recently power wash,stainless appliances,refrigerator, and much more.Close to theme park Kemah Boardwalk,146 for quick and easy commutes,shoppping center and waterfront restaurants.Walking distance to the neighborhood's park with its pool,park, greenspace, playground and community center. Perfect for anyone!Welcome Home!
